5086電腦輔助語言教學的理論與實務
106/07/21 04:33:48





105學年第二學期東海大學教師授課計劃表
Course Plan of Tunghai University



一.課程基本資料 Course Information


開課系所Department
(研)外文系


課程名稱Course Title

中文 (Chinese) : 電腦輔助語言教學的理論與實務

英文 (English) : Introduction to  Computer-Assisted Languages Learning: Theory and Practice



必選修類別Required/Elective
選修
先修課程Prerequisites



學分數Credits
0 - 3


先修課程說明Prerequisites instruction



課程概述(系所共同性目標)Course Description
The course is designed to present an overview of the field of computer-assisted language learning (CALL), computer-mediated communication (CMC), and second language acquisition (SLA). In this course, the trends of CALL, CMC, and core theories of SLA will be introduced in order to equip students with the basic concepts and tools necessary for more advanced study in research related to technology and second/foreign language teaching and learning. This course will cover issues and problems in current CALL and CMC research and provide a historical framework of the development of the field. Through discussions, activities, and projects, students will critically evaluate recent CALL research, discuss issues in the current literature, develop technology-enhanced materials, and apply them to classroom teaching.


本課程是否為英語授課
是


課程英文簡介
The goal of this course is to help pre-service teachers have a better understanding of computer-assisted language learning.


二、教師相關資料 Instruction Information





授課教師資料


