四、課程內涵與學生核心能力之對應Correspondence Between CourseContents and Core Competency





序No.
課程內涵與學生核心能力之對應Correspondence Between CourseContents and Core Competency>


1
understand the nature of language, language learning, language teaching, and language assessment; 瞭解語言、語言學習與教學、語言評量的本質



2
understand and apply principles and practices that promote language learning,        teaching, and assessment; 瞭解並應用能提昇語言學習與教學和語言評量的原理與實務



3
teach English to a variety of students, especially at the secondary school level; 教導不同級別的學生英文，特別是中學生



4
reflect upon teaching practice and develop professionally;  進行教學反思及專業成長



5
think analytically, critically, and independently; 作分析、批判、獨立性的思考



6
conduct research independently about educational phenomena;  獨立進行教育現象研究


 









